Series & Collection: Salfeet Women's Charity Sub-collection 2: Documents and Papers from the 1st Palestinian Social Conference  |  The Salfeet Women Charity Collection
Description (Eng): A copy of a research paper entitled "The Social Drivers behind Migration from the West Bank." It was presented during the First Palestinian Social Conference which was held in al-Quds in 1981 and was organised by the Federation of Charitable Associations.
